The paper deals with bugs in blockchain-based smart contracts, which are related to the dynamic ordering of contract events. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of computer security (cs.CR), software engineering (cs.SE), programming languages (cs.PL), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and logic in computer science (cs.LO).
